# Space-Track.org credentials — required ONLY for `npm run fetch-fullcat`
# (the full ~28k catalogue). Register free at https://www.space-track.org
# CelesTrak (`npm run fetch-tle`) needs no credentials.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in your account:
SPACETRACK_USER=you@example.com
SPACETRACK_PASS=your-password
